Docs.summary: Represents the class derived from the PortalSiteMapNode class, used to wrap nodes of type CachedObjectSiteMapNode.

remarks.para: Nodes of type CachedObjectSiteMapNode must be wrapped by a ProxySiteMapNode object for security trimming and to work effectively.
